{"tid":1918904,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"9:30  31台 《流感奪命五千萬》","createTime":"2020-03-10T11:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T05:16:16.000Z","uid":37554,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"31d8abeb39c31e6dc0a16fa4da8aede5f528d027","tid":1918904,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:48:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aCVqGzZemX0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaCVqGzZemX0&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSlKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=79efb2b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aCVqGzZemX0</a><br />\n1918年，第一次世界大戰結束。數以百萬計的人死亡，世界因戰爭而筋疲力盡。可惜不消多久，新一輪的恐慌席捲全球，一種可怕的病毒出現，殺死了超過五千萬人，這就是西班牙流感。這紀錄片透過個案重組與及目擊者，包括科學家、醫護人員、軍人、普羅市民和政客的親身經歷，再一次將昔日的慘況呈現觀眾眼前，讓大家了解當年人類如何面對病毒的襲擊和尋找治療的方法。一個世紀後的今天，希望人類藉此歷史吸取教訓，有助大家應對未來全球流感的大爆發。<br />\n雙語廣播：粵語/英語 (電視版)<br />\n播放頻道：港台電視 31、31A<br />\n播出時間：<br />\n(首播)2020年3月10日 星期二 晚上9時30分<br />\n(重溫)2020年3月11日 星期三 凌晨12時      <br />\n           2020年3月11日 星期三 中午12時"},{"pid":"6f18c2bd857adca183bd4e0082dab662855ee878","tid":1918904,"uid":39181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T12:01:38.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"9db99980a2c218fc723d8b48197c062cefffa7e9","tid":1918904,"uid":39181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26c86912f2047486b79c8dd2dfa9935e04f2a9c","tid":1918904,"uid":39181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:33:21.000Z","msg":"以前既歐洲人識戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e835572a436e6d54bf867f4d629fc1f1aa7b338","tid":1918904,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394d791dd288efdeedd233df7f737d026c0fa3c6","tid":1918904,"uid":53922,"